<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>day and night • day or night</xh5><p> <i>day and night—</i>continually; all the time: We worked <u>day and night</u> to finish the project before the end of the month.</p><p> <i>day or night—</i>at any time whatever: The Internet is the best shopping mall in the world and one that you can visit <u>day or night</u>.</p> </entry>
